{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"InputEvent()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent/InputEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent\"><code>InputEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><em><code>InputEvent()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent/data\"><code>data</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent/dataTransfer\"><code>dataTransfer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent/inputType\"><code>inputType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent/isComposing\"><code>isComposing</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/InputEvent/getTargetRanges\"><code>getTargetRanges()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>构造函数&nbsp;<strong><code>InputEvent()</code></strong>&nbsp;返回一个新创建的&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent\"><code>InputEvent</code></a>&nbsp;对象。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"> <em>event</em> = new InputEvent(<em>typeArg</em>, <em>inputEventInit</em>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"typearg\"><em>typeArg</em></dt>\n <dd>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> ，表示事件的名称。</dd>\n <dt id=\"inputeventinit\"><em>inputEventInit</em><span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n</dl>\n\n<p>一个&nbsp;<code>InputEventInit</code>&nbsp;字典，有以下字段：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>inputType</code>（可选），指定可编辑内容更改类型的字符串，例如插入、删除或格式化文本。</li>\n <li><code>data</code>（可选），包含要插入的字符的字符串。如果更改未插入文本（例如删除字符时），则其可能为空字符串。</li>\n <li><code>dataTransfer</code>（可选），一个&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer\"><code>DataTransfer</code></a>&nbsp;对象，其中包含有关添加到可编辑内容，或从可编辑内容中删除的富文本或纯文本数据的信息。</li>\n <li><code>isComposing</code>（可选），一个布尔值，指示事件是组合会话的一部分，这意味着它在&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/compositionstart_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">compositionstart (en-US)</a></code>&nbsp;事件之后，但在&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/compositionend_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">compositionend (en-US)</a></code>&nbsp;事件之前。默认值为&nbsp;<code>false</code>。</li>\n <li><code>ranges</code>（可选），一个静态&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a> 数组，如果输入事件没有被取消，它将受到对 DOM 的更改的影响。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em><code>InputEventInit</code></em><em> 字典也接受来自 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/UIEvent\" title=\"UIEventInit\"><code>UIEventInit</code></a> 以及 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/Event\" title=\"EventInit\"><code>EventInit</code></a> 字典的值。</em></p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.InputEvent.InputEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent/InputEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考","title":"参考","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent\"><code>InputEvent</code></a>，它构造的对象所属的接口。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参考","id":"参考"}],"summary":"构造函数 InputEvent() 返回一个新创建的 InputEvent 对象。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"InputEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/inputevent/inputevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/inputevent/inputevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent","title":"InputEvent"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent/InputEvent","title":"InputEvent()"}],"pageTitle":"InputEvent() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}